dataItinearies.name: Day trip to Cerro Cathedral
dataItinearies.collaborator: Ana Alfonzo
dataItinearies.profilePic: https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/mytinerary-6ce01.appspot.com/o/personas%2Fdescarga%20(2).jpg?alt=media&token=a5e46594-5575-4c18-95d9-19118a1753c7
dataItinearies.Description: Discover the largest ski centre in the southern hemisphere with this day trip to Cerro Catedral. A must-see for all mountain lovers!

dataItinearies.name: Tour panorámico por Buenos Aires
dataItinearies.collaborator: Catalina Roman
dataItinearies.profilePic: https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/mytinerary-6ce01.appspot.com/o/personas%2Fdescarga%20(1).jpg?alt=media&token=e25fca7c-497b-43c7-afca-583a7a824a1f
dataItinearies.Description: On this bus tour, we'll explore every side of Buenos Aires, enjoying the main districts, avenues, and monuments of the city. The visit is the perfect introduction to the city of Tango.

dataItinearies.name: Explore Rio de Janeiro
dataItinearies.collaborator: Silvia Santos
dataItinearies.profilePic: https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/mytinerary-6ce01.appspot.com/o/personas%2Fdescarga%20(1).jpg?alt=media&token=e25fca7c-497b-43c7-afca-583a7a824a1f
dataItinearies.Description: Discover Rio de Janeiro with this complete tour of what is affectionately known as the ‘carioca’ city. The Christ the Redeemer Statue, Sugarloaf Mountain and the Maracana stadium are just some of the places you will encounter on this fantastic tour!
placesToVisit: Avenue in front of Copacabana beach.
The Metropolitan Cathedral of Saint Sebastian

dataItinearies.name: Full day tour to Angra dos Reis and Ilha Grande
dataItinearies.collaborator: Silvia Santos
dataItinearies.profilePic: https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/mytinerary-6ce01.appspot.com/o/personas%2Fdescarga%20(1).jpg?alt=media&token=e25fca7c-497b-43c7-afca-583a7a824a1f
dataItinearies.Description: Discover the Brazilian paradise of Angra dos Reis and enjoy bathing on its heavenly beaches. Take a wonderful boat ride in a traditional Brazilian boat around the islands of the bay and taste delicious local food.

dataItinearies.name: Full day of Florence
dataItinearies.collaborator: Di Marco Diego
dataItinearies.profilePic: https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/mytinerary-6ce01.appspot.com/o/personas%2FDi%20marco.jpg?alt=media&token=d9901475-3ea7-481e-97c2-3739515903ce
dataItinearies.Description: The historic centre of Florence, capital of Tuscany, is an open-air museum dedicated to the Renaissance. Discover its past with this free tour!

dataItinearies.name: The Vatican Museums and Sistine Chapel
dataItinearies.collaborator: Di Marco Diego
dataItinearies.profilePic: https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/mytinerary-6ce01.appspot.com/o/personas%2FDi%20marco.jpg?alt=media&token=d9901475-3ea7-481e-97c2-3739515903ce
dataItinearies.Description: With this ticket you'll get access to the Sistine Chapel first thing in the morning, avoiding all the crowds. Then you can enjoy the other Vatican Museums at your leisure!
